message:
Recently we had the pleasure of working with a survivor-led NGO. It was not a new organization just new to us. It was great working with them because they understood some challenges we had without having to explain in detail. 
 
“I love when people that have been through hell walk out of the flames carrying buckets of water for those still consumed by the fire.” – Stephanie Sparkles⠀
#SurvivorLeaders #CommunityLeaders #CreatingChange #LeadingByExample #SupportingOthers #HelpingWithoutExpectations
